Comment:
Moderate threshold was adjusted up from calculated moderate in order to get rid of moderate severity in shrublands/wetlands.

Burn area has multiple land covers including forests, shrubland, and dwarf shrublands.

Moderate/High severity is in the higher biomass areas.  Low severity is in the lower biomass areas.

Pre-scene is over a month away from anniversary date.  Pre-image is best image of high quality that could be found.
